
add this in pom.xml: 	
	<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-actuator</artifactId>
	</dependency>
		
how to reach : via Browser -> http://localhost:8080/actuator


What/Why : It provides to monitor and manage your application in your production. Thus, there is no code.
what to Monitor: 
	- beans: Complete List of Spring beans in your Application.
	- health: information about Application's health.
	- metrics: Application metrics
	- mappings: Details around Request Mappings
	- and More